Package: libltdl
Section: libs
Priority: optional
Architecture: ARCH
Depends: libc (>= 1.1.8), ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: System independent dlopen wrapper for GNU libtool
 This package provides libltdl, a shared library which aims at hiding the 
 various difficulties of dlopening libraries from programmers.

Package: libltdl-dev
Section: libdevel
Priority: optional
Architecture: ARCH
Depends: libc-dev, libtool (= ${binary:Version}), libltdl-dev (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Development headers and static library for libltdl
 This package provides header files required for development using
 libltdl.

Package: libtool
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Architecture: ARCH
Depends: libc (>= 1.1.8), ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: Generic library support script
 This package provides GNU libtool, a generic library support script.  
 .
 Libtool hides the complexity of generating special library types (such as 
 shared libraries) behind a consistent interface.

Package: libtool-doc
Section: doc
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Recommends: man-db
Depends: libtool (= ${binary:Version})
Description: documentation for libtool
 This package provides info and man pages for libtool.
